    </p>
    <h3><em>Mobile Penicillin Laboratory, Model</em>, 1943</h3>

    <p>
    Mixed media model<br />    20 x 61 x 61 cm<br />        The Archive of Bertrand Goldberg, gifted by his children through his estate, RX23664/158.2</p>
        
